        <item>
            <title>腾讯新游戏《Light of Motiram》，被指抄袭《地平线》+《芒亨》+《幻兽帕鲁》</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/new-tencent-game-accused-of-ripping-off-sonys-horizon/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=new-tencent-game-accused-of-ripping-off-sonys-horizon</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/new-tencent-game-accused-of-ripping-off-sonys-horizon/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 07:00:53 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Pokemon]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[腾讯]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1277858</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>中国腾讯旗下子公司 Polaris Quest 所开发的新游戏《Light of Motiram》最近引起争议，有舆论指游戏抄袭 Sony 的经典作品《Horizon Zero Dawn》（地平线，期待黎明）与《Horizon Forbidden West》（地平线，西域禁地）。有玩家指游戏画面、玩法设计、故事背景及角色设置，也与 Sony 的《Horizon》系列有著诸多雷同之处。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278093" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/l11732793630767-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/l11732793630767-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/l11732793630767.jpg 888w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：IGN</p><p>《Light of Motiram》是一款多人在线开放世界生存游戏，背景设定在自然与机械交织的末日世界，玩家在充斥著机械生物的荒野中重建人类文明，并与「机械兽」对抗求生。从预告片及游戏画面来看，游戏中的女主角形象及其动作设计，几乎与《Horizon》中的艾洛伊如出一辙。而游戏中的机械生物，无论是其造型、特征，还是战斗方式，均与《Horizon》中的机械兽极为相似，甚至整体后末日的风格也有著惊人的相近之处。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278095" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125629-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125629-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125629.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：IGN</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278096" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125637-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125637-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125637.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：IGN</p><p>众多玩家指出，《Light of Motiram》在游戏机制、基建建设资源收集等方面，与《Monster Hunter》及《Palworld》也有显著的相似性。尤其是《Palworld》涉嫌「抄袭」《Pokemon》元素而一度引发争议后，类似情况无疑再度成为焦点。更有玩家在 Steam 平台上直言不讳指这款游戏几乎可以视作《Horizon 3》，并用「令人作呕的抄袭」来形容其设计。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">Disgusting Rip-Off</p><p>— Pirate King (@Maanlosi) <a href="https://twitter.com/Maanlosi/status/1862086620561789224?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">November 28, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278097" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125642-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125642-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125642.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：IGN</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278098" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125648-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125648-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125648.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：IGN</p><p>目前游戏开发方尚未对这些指控给予正式回应，但随著争议的不断升温，无疑再度点燃游戏业界对创意原创性与版权保护的讨论。作为《Horizon》系列的发行商，Sony 会否对此事采取法律行动亦成为了业界与玩家热议的焦点。值得一提的是，Sony 目前正开发一款基于《Horizon》世界观的多人在线服务游戏。尽管争议未息，《Light of Motiram》仍会于 2025 年在 PC 与手机平台推出，支援跨平台游玩。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278099" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125653-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125653-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125653.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：IGN</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278100" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125700-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125700-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125700.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：IGN</p><div style="padding: 75% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="h-lol-1732793707107-ezgif.com-gif-to-mp4-converter (1)" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1034405724?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲影片来源：IGN</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.ign.com/articles/new-tencent-game-accused-of-ripping-off-sonys-horizon-series?">IGN</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/new-tencent-game-accused-of-ripping-off-sonys-horizon/game-channel/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
