        </item>
        <item>
            <title>香港宽频推 GigaFast 宽频，配指定 TP-Link 路由器可遥距监测 + 管理网络</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/hkbn-tplink-new-coop/wireless-home/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=hkbn-tplink-new-coop</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/hkbn-tplink-new-coop/wireless-home/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 02:30:33 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[家居无线]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[路由器]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[hkbn]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[TP-LINK]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[香港宽频]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1278020</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>相信大家都有面对过一个问题：家中的 Wi-Fi 网络出现不知甚么问题，反正就是上网突然变慢甚至不能上网，但碰巧家人在家但你不在，向你致电求助你又难以遥距解决。香港宽频今日就伙拍 TP-Link 推出 GigaFast 宽频，只要配合 TP-Link 指定路由器，香港宽频客服就可以遥距为用家解决网络问题，以后家人即使遇到上网问题，也更加容易随时找到人解决了。</p><h2>暂需配合 Aginet 路由器日后支援更多</h2><p>今次香港宽频推出的 GigaFast 宽频服务，属于 5Gbps / 10Gbps 速度的固网宽频，月费为 $698 起，暂时只支援 TP-Link 的 Aginet EB810v 路由器，不过官方表示日后支援的款式会更多。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278024" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_153835-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_153835-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_153835.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲香港宽频伙拍 TP-Link 推出全新 GigaFast 宽频服务，速度最低亦有 5Gbps，亦支援最新的 Wi-Fi 7 制式。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278025" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_153744-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_153744-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_153744.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲不过暂时此服务只支援 TP-Link 的 Aginet 系列路由器。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278026" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_153737-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_153737-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_153737.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲现场所见电脑以 LAN 线接驳 Aginet EB810v 路由器，配合 10Gbps GigaFast 宽频服务，下载及上载速度分别达到 8142.81Mbps 及 7692.78Mbps，表现十分理想。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278027" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_153752-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_153752-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_153752.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而配合支援 Wi-Fi 7 网络的手机，无线接驳下载及上载速度亦分别达到 3145Mbps 及 3440Mbps。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278029" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_163150-694x425.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="425" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_163150-694x425.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_163150.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278030" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_163156-694x440.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="440" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_163156-694x440.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_163156.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲香港宽频的 GigaFast 宽频服务暂时支援 5Gbps 及 10Gbps 两个速度服务，月费为 $698 起，当中除了包括固网宽频服务外，亦包括借出 Aginet BE22000 Wi-Fi 7 路由器、F-Secure 防护服务及 Priority Plus 一站式家居 Wi-Fi 方案。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278028" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_162539-694x424.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="424" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_162539-694x424.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_162539.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278031" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_162805-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_162805-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_162805.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲官方更表示日后 GigaFast 宽频服务更会设有 25Gbps 速度选择，亦可支援更多 TP-Link 路由器，不过暂时均只支援 Aginet 系列，Deco 等系列就暂未支援得到。</p><h2>24 x 7 为用户解决网络问题</h2><p>而配合香港宽频的 Priority Plus 一站式家居 Wi-Fi 方案，不但用家可将家中 Wi-Fi 网络升级至最新的 Wi-Fi 7 制式，更可结合 Aginet Unified Cloud（TAUC）平台，即使用家遇上任何网络问题，只要联络香港宽频的 CS，职员验证用家身份后，就可以遥距实时监测及管理用家家中的路由器，并主动侦测用户 Wi-Fi 的网络健康状况，如有异常更可透过云端管理平台遥距诊断及修正，省回额外上门检查的工夫。更重要是这服务是 24 x 7 提供，即使用户深夜遇上网络问题，也可以即时找到「救兵」解决问题，确实十分方便。假如合约期内遇上未能解决的问题，更可享受专业人员上门「一换一」的路由器更换服务，确实十分体贴。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278032" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_154051-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_154051-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_154051.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278033" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_154100-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_154100-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_154100.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲配合 Priority Plus 服务，用家一旦遇上网络问题，香港宽频职员即可遥距监测用户的网络情况，并诊断有否出现任何问题。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278034" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_161410-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_161410-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_161410.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278035" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_162922-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_162922-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_162922.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲如果遇上问题，Aginet 的云端管理系统就会打出分数，香港宽频的职员即可知道问题所在，并可透过电话或网络遥距为用户提供解决方案，或直接为用家解决问题，省回上门检查的工夫及时间，即使深夜遇上问题亦可找到职员为用户解决。</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/hkbn-tplink-new-coop/wireless-home/">香港宽频推 GigaFast 宽频，配指定 TP-Link 路由器可遥距监测 + 管理网络</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
