        <item>
            <title>【报价】vivo X200 系列香港正式发布，港行靓镜手机 + 眩光问题有解决？+ 开售详情公布</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/vivo-x200series-hk-launch/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=vivo-x200series-hk-launch</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/vivo-x200series-hk-launch/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 01:59:47 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[vivo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[X200]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[X200 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1277998</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>vivo 在一个月前，就在中国发布了新一代的旗舰手机 X200 系列，而当中的 X200 及 X200 Pro 之后亦宣布会推出国际版，而这两部 vivo 新机今日就正式在香港发布。究竟这部配备超靓「蔡司」镜的手机表现如何？之前的眩光问题有没有解决？开售详情如何？就让 Edward 带大家到现场看看吧。</p><h2>新一代旗舰靓镜依然</h2><p>今次 vivo 推出的 X200 及 X200 Pro，基本上与国行的 X200 及 X200 Pro 一样，同样配备了超靓的「蔡司」镜头，分别是前者配备了均为 5,000 万像素的主摄镜、超广角镜及超级长焦镜，而后者就除了配备相同的超广角镜外，亦内建了拥有大感光元件的 5,000 万像素主摄镜及高达 2 亿像素的 APO 超级长焦镜。另外，两机均内建了 MTK 天玑 9400 处理器，亦均支援 IP68 及 IP69 防水防尘级数。电量方面，X200 内建了 5,800mAh 容量电池并支援 90W 有线快充，而 X200 Pro 除了内建更大容量的 6,000mAh 电池外，亦支援 90W 有线及 30W 无线快充。至于较高阶的 X200 Pro 的完整使用体验，大家可以 <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/22/vivo-x200pro-chinaversion-review/review-2/">&lt;点按此&gt;</a> 浏览笔者早前测试的国行版本。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278002" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_123923-1-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_123923-1-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_123923-1.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲vivo 今日在香港正式推出 X200（左）及 X200 Pro（右）两部旗舰靓镜手机。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278003" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_135822-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_135822-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_135822.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲两部 X200 系列同样依然配备了「蔡司」靓镜。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278004" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130439-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130439-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130439.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278005" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130510-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130510-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130510.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲不过相机规格上自然是较贵较高阶的 X200 Pro 更加吸引。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278006" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125613-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125613-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125613.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲X200 系列亦是现时市场少有仍会内建自家定制影像晶片的手机机款。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278007" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125445-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125445-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125445.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲X200 及 X200 Pro 均内建了 MTK 最新推出的天玑 9400 处理器。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278008" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125755-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125755-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125755.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲两机亦同样支援 IP68 及 IP69 防水防尘级数。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278009" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125749-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125749-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125749.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲此外，两部 X 系新机均内建了大容量电池，尤其是较高阶的 X200 Pro，不但容量较高，亦同时支援有线及无线快充。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278010" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125826_-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125826_-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125826_.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲亦与其他旗舰手机一样，支援不同的 AI 功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278011" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130523-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130523-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130523.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278012" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130555-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130555-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130555.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至于 X200 及 X200 Pro 的其他特点及功能，大家可参晚上面两张相片。</p><h2>眩光问题有否解决？似乎有改善</h2><p>另外，早前国行版本 vivo X200 Pro 推出时，有些用家就反映手机虽然镜头质素出色，但就似乎出现官方称为「画外眩光」的问题。官方亦承认因为今代镜头模组比上代薄，但就塞入超大感光元件及超大光圈（f/1.57）的主摄镜，导致更大光圈及进光量亦带来更易触发画外眩光，确实属于硬件上设计的问题。今日香港记招笔者亦向 vivo 查询港行推出时此问题有否解决？而香港 vivo 亦承认确实有此问题，但其实官方会在今年内向用家以 OTA 形式发送可以减轻或消除眩光的软件，届时用家安装后眩光问题就有望可改善。不过官方表示如果用上此补丁，就可能会牺牲一定像素，所以如何选择就视乎用家的个人喜好了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278013" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_132734-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_132734-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_132734.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278014" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_132837-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_132837-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_132837.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲vivo 已为 X200 系列推出了改善画外眩光问题的修改档，香港 vivo 表示在今年内会以 OTA 形式推送给用家安装。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278015" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_133040-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_133040-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_133040.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲安装后，在相机设定中会见到「拍照眩光减弱」功能，开启后官方表示可以有效减弱之前的眩光问题，不过是否属实就有待日后借得真机后再为大家实试了。</p><h2>开售详情公布香港「独家」有蓝色</h2><p>至于开售详情方面，vivo X200 及 X200 Pro 均已开始接受预订，并会在 12 月 1 日，即系本周日正式开卖。定价方面，X200 为 $6,998，而 X200 Pro 则为 $8,998。值得留意的是，港行 X200 设有星云黑及森林绿两只颜色，而 X200 Pro 方面除了设有所有有开售国际版均有售的星云黑及地玄钛色外，更暂时是中国市场以外「独家」有卖海洋蓝版本，而笔者现场望过，这个海洋蓝色确实有点特别，不过如果真要说，笔者觉得地玄钛色似乎更加低调漂亮。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278016" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130714-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130714-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130714.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲推出详情方面，vivo X200 定价为 $6,998，而 X200 Pro 定价则为 $8,998。前者设有星云黑及森林绿两只颜色，而后者就设有星云黑、地玄钛及海洋蓝 3 款颜色。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278017" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_131822-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_131822-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_131822.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲当中尤以海洋蓝这款机身颜色，香港是中国地区以外唯一有推出此颜色的地方，不过笔者现场望过实机，确实特别但不算太吸睛。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278018" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_135802-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_135802-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_135802.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲相对地笔者觉得地玄钛色似乎更加漂亮，不过设计就相对较低调。</p><br /><b>
]]>
